- Added a default fleet for new Windows MDM enrollments (Fleet Premium). IT admins can pick the fleet that hosts enrolling through user-driven Windows MDM enrollment (Windows Autopilot, Entra join) are automatically assigned to, via **Settings > Integrations > MDM > Windows MDM**, the `mdm.windows_enrollment.default_fleet` config setting, or GitOps. The fleet is assigned before the Autopilot Enrollment Status Page runs, so the default fleet's software, scripts, and configuration profiles apply during out-of-box setup.
